      <title>亿万富翁阿达尼的绿色部门计划明年通过债务筹集 20 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/gautam-adani-s-green-unit-plans-to-raise-2-billion-via-debt-next-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，亿万富翁高塔姆·阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 的可再生能源部门计划明年筹集至少 20 亿美元，其中大部分是新债务，因为该部门将利用债权人对其雄心勃勃的扩张计划重新燃起的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/gautam-adani-s-green-unit-plans-to-raise-2-billion-via-debt-next-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 09:31:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本将向美国出售导弹以放宽武器出口规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/japan-to-sell-missiles-to-us-in-relaxation-of-arms-export-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本政府表示，周五放宽了对武器出口的限制，并正式批准了向美国出口爱国者导弹的计划，满足其盟友的要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/japan-to-sell-missiles-to-us-in-relaxation-of-arms-export-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 09:22:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本计划下一财年债务发行量减少 10%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/japan-plans-10-reduction-in-debt-sales-next-fiscal-year-lqgdry11</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本计划在 4 月 1 日开始的财年中减少约 10% 的债务销售，政府试图降低世界上最大的发达国家债务负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/japan-plans-10-reduction-in-debt-sales-next-fiscal-year-lqgdry11</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 08:39:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国沪深300指数结束2012年以来最长单周下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/china-s-csi-300-index-caps-longest-weekly-losing-streak-since-2012</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于房地产行业持续陷入困境，中国经济复苏未能获得动力，中国股市在 2023 年结束时看起来将表现惨淡，这与投资者在年初对新冠疫情后强劲反弹的高预期不符。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/china-s-csi-300-index-caps-longest-weekly-losing-streak-since-2012</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 07:32:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
