      <title>由于红海袭击扰乱全球流动，石油将每周上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-22</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于红海袭击迫使数百艘船只采取更安全但更长的航线，延迟了石油货物的交付，石油价格延续了两个月来的最大单周涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-22</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 00:11:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>航运和能源公司正在采取哪些措施应对红海混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/what-tanker-and-energy-companies-are-saying-about-red-sea-route</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Kuehne+Nagel 表示，一百多艘集装箱船正在绕非洲航行，以避免红海发生暴力事件。马士基表示，工作组可能需要几周时间才能全面投入运作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/what-tanker-and-energy-companies-are-saying-about-red-sea-route</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 17:31:42 GMT</pubDate>
